          "doi": "10.1101/2023.11.30.23299240",
          "title": "Fitness models provide accurate short-term forecasts of SARS-CoV-2 variant frequency",
          "authorString": "Abousamra E, Figgins MD, Bedford T.",
          "authorList": {
            "author": [
              {
                "fullName": "Abousamra E",
                "firstName": "Eslam",
                "lastName": "Abousamra",
